Package: GaugeRNA
Type: Package
Title: GaugeRNA: A Gauge-Invariant Audit Framework for RNA-seq Differential Expression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("GaugeRNA", "Research Group", email = "gaugerna@research.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A gauge-invariant audit framework for RNA-seq differential expression analysis.
    Computes Gauge Instability Scores (GIS) to quantify the sensitivity of differential
    expression results to arbitrary normalization choices (gauge choices). Provides
    gamma projection, gauge decomposition, and automated audit report generation.
    Designed for reproducible validation of RNA-seq differential expression findings.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
